 desde un Samsung la variable conn me devuelve lo correcto, pero si lo hago desde otro, esta variable es null.</p><p>Muchas gracias</p> </section></div> </article><ol class="children"><li class="comment byuser comment-author-hidden2 bypostauthor odd alt depth-2" id="li-comment-643"> <article id="comment-643" class="comment"><div class="comment-avatar"> <img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/08895492876c3a8160011ac0ef0c3d1c?s=100&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D100&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-100 photo' height='100' width='100'/></div><div class="text"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"> <cite class="fn"><a href="http://www.elbauldelprogramador.com" rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Alejandro Alcalde</a> <span> Post author</span></cite><a href="/conectar-base-de-datos-sql-server-2008/#comment-643"><time datetime="2013-04-25T08:15:20+00:00">2013/04/25 at 08:15</time></a><span class="sep">/</span><a class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-643' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-643", "643", "respond", "182")'>Reply</a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>No sabría decirte, yo solo la he usado con Android. Qué dispositivo es?</p> </section></div> </article><ol class="children"><li class="comment even depth-3" id="li-comment-645"> <article id="comment-645" class="comment"><div class="comment-avatar"> <img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/4cf34c5c8d007330ae4103a31f130a27?s=100&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D100&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-100 photo' height='100' width='100'/></div><div class="text"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"> <cite class="fn">Miguel </cite><a href="/conectar-base-de-datos-sql-server-2008/#comment-645"><time datetime="2013-04-25T08:19:10+00:00">2013/04/25 at 08:19</time></a><span class="sep">/</span><a class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-645' onclick='return